{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id90bfbe71-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s6591"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6591"},"text":"§ 6591.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" “United States assistance” defined","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this part, the term “United States assistance” means development and other economic assistance, including assistance made available under the following provisions of law:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id90bfbe72-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s6591/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Chapter 1 of part I of the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2151"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2151","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] (relating to development assistance)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id90bfbe73-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s6591/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Chapter 4 of part II of the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2346"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2346","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] (relating to the economic support fund)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id90bfbe74-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s6591/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Chapter 10 of part I of the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2293"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2293","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] (relating to the Development Fund for Africa)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id90bfbe75-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s6591/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Chapter 11 of part I of the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2295"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2295","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] (relating to assistance for the independent states of the former Soviet Union)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id90bfbe76-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s6591/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Support for East European Democracy Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s5401"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 5401","children":[],"tail":" et seq.)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id90bfbe77-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/277/dG"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–277, div. G","children":[],"tail":", subdiv. A, title XV, § 1521, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-21"},"text":"Oct. 21, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/2681-794"},"text":"112 Stat. 2681–794","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id90bfbe78-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id90bfbe79-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id90bfbe7a-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Foreign Assistance Act of 1961, referred to in pars. (1) to (4), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/195"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–195","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1961-09-04"},"text":"Sept. 4, 1961","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/75/424"},"text":"75 Stat. 424","children":[],"tail":". Chapters 1, 10, and 11 of part I of the Act are classified generally to parts I (§ 2151 et seq.), X (§ 2293 et seq.), and XI (§ 2295 et seq.), respectively, of subchapter I of chapter 32 of this title. Chapter 4 of part II of the Act is classified generally to part IV (§ 2346 et seq.) of subchapter II of chapter 32 of this title. For provisions deeming references to part I of subchapter I to include a reference to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2293"},"text":"section 2293 of this title","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2293/d/1"},"text":"section 2293(d)(1) of this title","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2151"},"text":"section 2151 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Support for East European Democracy Act, referred to in par. (5), probably means the Support for East European Democracy (SEED) Act of 1989, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/179"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–179","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1989-11-28"},"text":"Nov. 28, 1989","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/103/1298"},"text":"103 Stat. 1298","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 63 (§ 5401 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s5401"},"text":"section 5401 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
